# Angular Rules

- Use standalone components/directives/pipes (Angular 17+).
- Default to `ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush`.
- Prefer DI via `inject()` when it reduces boilerplate.
- Templates: use `async` pipe instead of manual subscriptions.
- Always add `trackBy` for `ngFor` lists.
- Use `NgOptimizedImage` for static images (no base64).
- Use the `host` object instead of `@HostBinding/@HostListener`.
- Prefer semantic HTML and proper ARIA attributes.
- Use signals for local reactive state where appropriate.
